mimic: Replies with everything written after the initial command.
help: Gives information about the target command.
stanch: Used for setting variables of a server. Named this way because set sounds wrong.
commands: Replies with every command the bot has, sorted by permission.
objectify: Adds an insult to the insult list, no matter how shitty or inappropriate.
unobjectify: Removes an insult from the insult list, I guess.
kill: Kills a target user with a HiLaRiOuS rAnDoM eVeNt
stats: Shows the stats of either you or a target user.
stimulate: Give yourself a shock for bonus {0.sd.currency_name}.
change: A command for a bunch of user customization commands.
objectirray: Lists every insult for the current server.
save: A funny command that's here because I'm a shit programmer apparently.
rawsend: A not so funny command used for debugging.
cash: Tells you how much money you have. Less spammy than {msg.sd.prefix}stats
simulate: Simulates a user. Requires a level of cache for the user.
fullCache: Fully caches a channel. Can take way too long for most commands.
clearCache: Removes all caches for testing purposes.
flip: Bet and flip a coin! Test your luck -- but beware of sides.
